  "body": "<!--\r\nNeed help?\r\nRefer to our contributing guidelines for additional information about making a good issue:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/.github/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nFollowing our last regenesis on 14th November 2021 we verified contracts in both `optimistic-kovan` and `optimistic-mainnet` in `sourcify` and added support for optimism networks there:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/sourcify/pull/550\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/sourcify/pull/581\r\n\r\nThis process was manual for the regenesis however for future deployments we should automate that as part of the deploy process. \r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nUpdate the `DeployAndVerifyAndThen` script to add `sourcify` verification step.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n#1722 Adds source code verification on Etherscan during the deployment process. \r\n#1726 add better error handling into that process. \r\n#1534 Adds metadata settings to solc to enable contract verification on Sourcify\r\n",
